==German==
===Etymology===
Pejorative feminine form of [[Bulle]] (a derogative word for a male cop), influenced by the homophone [[Bulette]].

===Noun===
'''Bullette''' ''f''
# (derogative) a female [[cop]]
# (slang) a [[Berlin]] citizen

